148
00:22:11,189 --> 00:22:13,590
In math, there's three strands.

149
00:22:14,370 --> 00:22:16,491
In science, there's three strands as well.

150
00:22:17,833 --> 00:22:23,657
Based on the results of the skills survey, they select entry points or access skills.

151
00:22:24,317 --> 00:22:28,560
And then the students participate in the same content areas as the grade level pair.

152
00:22:28,620 --> 00:22:31,842
So if we're starting at grade three, it would be math and English.

153
00:22:32,743 --> 00:22:45,371
